column1: This file uses the system configured decimal symbol: ','
#    Not applicable   The measurement is not applicable in the current equipment state.
Normal           No code indicates a normal measurement, i.e. no warning or alarms
w    Raw warning      The measurement is outside the warning limits
W    Delayed warning  Same as raw warning but the measurement has been in this state for longer than the configured delay for this parameter group.
a    Raw alarm        The measurement is outside the alarm limits.
A    Delayed alarm    Same as raw alarm but the measurement has been in this state for longer than the configured delay for this parameter group.
*    Error            The ILS RMS is unable to provide the data. (Can be e.g. MO1212 failure or IIC error).
?    Unknown          The RS-232 protocol driver is currently not able to provide the data.
